<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">وطُلَّ مِنْهُ دَمُهُ أَيْ:</span> قُتِلا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>